description: These rolls are packed with veg and colours.
name: Rainbow Spring Rolls Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 4 stalks asparagus, sliced into thin sticks
8 sheets rice paper, thawed if frozen
1 medium carrot, peeled and sliced thinly lenghtways into sticks
1 head beetroot, sliced into thin sticks

recipeInstructions.text: Blanch and refresh the asparagus 30 seconds in boiling water then slice.
Dip the rice paper into warm water for 5 seconds.
Place the mixed veg sticks into the centre of a sheet of pastry, add some feta, fold over the edges and roll tightly.
